<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-12-03T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-12-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="587" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d587">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Pera</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-12-03"><hi rend="italic">December 3,
                                1895</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Guedjian delivered. Governor of Aleppo removed. Incident closed. Will
                            inform Guedjian if no trial before me is consented to that he is
                            required to depart from Ottoman Empire.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>